title: 216: 10 Takeaways from Week 5
itunes:title: 216: 10 Takeaways from Week 5
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dive into the ten biggest talking points around the league. Is Big Ben truly done (9:47)? Have the Jags found an identity (13:17)? Is Nelson Agholor the comeback player of the year (17:19)? All that and more in this episode of Move the Sticks presented by the Ford F-Series.
